OL,3,CNew mother stabbed to death by
OL,4,Cstranger while sleeping in bed with
OL,5,Cher baby
OL,7,FA man broke into the home of a young
OL,8,Fmother and fatally stabbed her as she
OL,9,Fslept in bed with her husband and
OL,10,Fthree month old baby, a court has
OL,11,Fheard.
OL,13,FDaniel Sean James allegedly attacked
OL,14,F24-year-old Kirandeep Kaur in Hayes on
OL,15,Fthe morning of July 12.
OL,17,FThe 46 year old then jumped out of a
OL,18,Fwindow and broke both ankles before
OL,19,Fbeing detained by police nearby, the
OL,20,FOld Bailey was told.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/5
