PN,37302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1784402277
OL,3,CNew mother stabbed to death by
OL,4,Cstranger while sleeping in bed with
OL,5,Cher baby
OL,7,FBefore the attack, James is said to
OL,8,Fhave walked through a playing field in
OL,9,FHayes dressed all in black and
OL,10,Fcarrying a large knife.
OL,12,FCCTV and doorbell cameras allegedly
OL,13,Fsaw James approaching three different
OL,14,Faddresses before coming up behind a
OL,15,Fyoung man and stabbing him in the back.
OL,17,FJust minutes later, at around 7.51am,
OL,18,Fhe is said to have kicked at the door
OL,19,Fof Kirandeep Kaur's home, breaking in
OL,20,Fwhile she was asleep in bed with her
OL,21,Fhusband and three month old baby.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/5
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1784402277
OL,3,CNew mother stabbed to death by
OL,4,Cstranger while sleeping in bed with
OL,5,Cher baby
OL,7,FProsecutor, Charlene Sumnall said the
OL,8,Fhusband awoke to a scream from his
OL,9,Fwife and saw a figure leaving the
OL,10,Fbedroom.
OL,12,FJust a few minutes later, James exited
OL,13,Fthe property on Uxbridge road by
OL,14,Fjumping out of a window, the court
OL,15,Fheard.
OL,17,FKirandeep Kaur suffered a stab wound
OL,18,Fto the chest and was pronounced dead
OL,19,Fat 8.26am.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/5
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
