OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1784402277
OL,3,CNew mother stabbed to death by
OL,4,Cstranger while sleeping in bed with
OL,5,Cher baby
OL,7,FThe Old Bailey was told that both
OL,8,Fvictims were complete strangers to the
OL,9,Fdefendant, who was treated in hospital
OL,10,Fbefore being taken into custody.
OL,12,FHe was subsequently charged with the
OL,13,Fmurder of Kirandeep Kaur, attempted
OL,14,Fmurder and having a blade.
OL,16,FOn Thursday, James, of Mercer Place,
OL,17,FPinner, west London, appeared in Court
OL,18,FOne of the Old Bailey by videolink
OL,19,Ffrom Wormwood Scrubs.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/5
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
