PN,37305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1784402277
OL,3,CNew mother stabbed to death by
OL,4,Cstranger while sleeping in bed with
OL,5,Cher baby
OL,7,FJudge Nigel Lickley KC set a plea
OL,8,Fhearing for October 1 and a
OL,9,Fprovisional three-week trial from
OL,10,FApril 5 next year.
OL,12,FJames spoke only to confirm his
OL,13,Fidentity and was remanded into custody.
OL,15,FFrom Westminster to Washington DC -
OL,16,Four political experts are across all
OL,17,Fthe latest key talking points. Listen
OL,18,Fto the latest episode below...
